title: Full Show (Eagles beat Vikings, Mike Evans suspended one game, Can Cooper Rush continue to lead the Cowboys to victory?)
description:
00:00 Eagles beat Vikings 24-7
23:03 Mike Evans suspended 1 game for altercation with Marshon Lattimore
53:06 Cowboys face Giants on MNF. Will Cooper Rush lead team to victory again?
1:08:20 Lakers hope that Dennis Schroder can return to form
1:19:46 Brady threw helmet and tablet during win over Saints. Was he just being competitive?
1:36:29 Stephen Jones says Dak might return by Week 4
1:44:16 Baker could reportedly be benched once Darnold returns from IR
1:50:53 Bills dominate Titans 41-7. Can this team win the Super Bowl?
1:55:41 Eagles' Darius Slay gifts ball to James Harden after interception
